sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Player A frontend
    participant B as Player B frontend
    participant S as Multiplayer service

    A->>S: POST /queue/join
    B->>S: POST /queue/join
    S-->>A: matched + matchId
    S-->>B: matched + matchId

    A->>S: GET /match/:id?playerId=A
    B->>S: GET /match/:id?playerId=B
    A->>S: subscribe_match
    B->>S: subscribe_match

    A->>S: POST action
    S->>S: validate action
    S->>S: mutate authoritative state
    S->>S: append ordered events
    S-->>A: player-scoped snapshot
    S-->>B: player-scoped snapshot
